data.description: BACK ON MARKET AT NO FAULT TO SELLERS. MOTIVATED SELLERS! Welcome to your dream home at 1817 Old Post Terrace in the heart of Woodbridge, Virginia! This exquisite end unit townhome boasts four spacious bedrooms, three and a half beautifully appointed bathrooms, and nearly 2000 total square feet of luxurious living space.  As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the stylishly updated kitchen and bathrooms featuring elegant quartz countertops. The kitchen is a chef's delight, complete with modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar – perfect for morning coffee or casual meals. Hardwood floors flow seamlessly throughout the main level, creating an inviting and warm atmosphere.  The abundant natural light streaming in through large windows enhances the inviting ambiance and provides a welcoming, sun-kissed environment. The open-concept living and dining areas are ideal for both entertaining and daily living, offering a flexible layout to suit your needs.  Upstairs, the primary bedroom suite is a tranquil retreat with its own private en-suite bathroom. Additional generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for family members, guests, or a home office. The updated bathrooms feature contemporary fixtures and finishes, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine.  Step outside to your private outdoor oasis where you can enjoy al fresco dining, gardening, or simply relaxing in the fresh air. This end unit property provides added privacy and outdoor space that is perfect for enjoying the Virginia seasons.  This fantastic community offers a wealth of amenities, including a sparkling community pool for those hot summer days, scenic walking and jogging paths for outdoor enthusiasts, and playgrounds for the little ones. Stay active with access to basketball and tennis courts for friendly games and fitness routines.  Located in a highly sought-after location, 1817 Old Post Terrace is just minutes away from shopping, dining, and major commuter routes, making it a prime location for those who desire both convenience and comfort. Don't miss your opportunity to own this exceptional home – schedule your showing today and make it yours!  Property Highlights:  Four bedrooms, three and a half bathrooms End unit Updated bathrooms and kitchen with quartz countertops Hardwood floors throughout Abundant natural light Private end unit with outdoor space Community pool, walking/jogging paths, playgrounds, basketball and tennis courts Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and commuter routes This property won't stay on the market for long, so don't wait! Contact us today to arrange a viewing and start living your dream in this Woodbridge gem.
